column3: BCPI Weights Agriculture - Potatoes: U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics - Producer Price Index; Cattle: (US$/100 lb.) Steer feeder, Oklahoma city; Hogs: (US$/100 lb.) Iowa – South Minnesota average; Wheat: (US$/bushel) U.S. #1 spring wheat, 14% protein; Barley: (US$/bushel) Saskatchewan aggregate spot price; Canola: (US$/bushel) #1 Canada in store Vancouver; Corn: (US$/bushel) U.S. corn #2, Central
BCPI Weights Brent - (US$/barrel) Brent front month futures, Intercontinental Exchange (ICE)
BCPI Weights Coal - (US$/tonne) long-term contract price for Canadian exports of metallurgical coal
BCPI Weights Fisheries - Finfish: Prices obtained from U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics/Haver Analytics; Shellfish: Prices obtained from U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics/Haver Analytics.

BCPI Weights Forestry - Pulp: (US$/tonne) northern bleached softwood Kraft pulp; Lumber: (US$/thousand board feet) spruce-pine-fir, 2"x4", f.o.b. at Prince George; Newsprint: (US$/ tonne) 30 pound newsprint price

BCPI Weights Metals and Minerals - Gold: (US$/oz.) Handy and Harman base price, N.Y.; Silver: (US$/oz.) Handy and Harman base price, N.Y.; Nickel: (US$/lb.) LME cash settlement; Copper: (US$/lb.) LME cash settlement; Aluminium: (US$/lb.) LME cash settlement; Zinc: (US$/lb.) LME cash settlement; Potash: (US$/tonne) standard potassium chloride, spot price, f.o.b. Vancouver; Lead: U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics - Producer Price Index; Iron: U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics - Producer Price Index
BCPI Weights Natural Gas - (US$/MMBtu) Henry Hub natural gas front month futures, New York Mercantile Exchange (NYMEX)
BCPI Weights Western Canada Select - (US$/barrel) front month futures of Net Energy Canadian Heavy Crude Oil index, Chicago Mercantile Exchange (CME)
BCPI Weights West Texas Intermediate - (US$/barrel) West Texas Intermediate front month futures, New York mercantile Exchange (NYMEX)
